#include <bits/stdc++.h> using namespace std; typedef long long LL; const int N = 2 2 2 2 2 2 ; const int M = 1 << 19; int n, q, l[N], r[N]; char s[N], f[N]; int t[M]; void modify(int L, int R, int x, int k = 1, int l = 1, int r = n) { if (L <= l && r <= R) { t[k] = (r - l + 1) * x; return; } int h = l + r >> 1; if (t[k] == 0) t[k << 1] = 0, t[k << 1 | 1] = 0; if (t[k] == r - l + 1) t[k << 1] = h - l + 1, t[k << 1 | 1] = r - h; if (L <= h) m o d i f y ( L , R, x, k << 1, l, h); if (h < R) m o d i f y ( L , R, x, k << 1 | 1, h + 1, r); t[k] = t[k << 1] + t[k << 1 | 1]; } int query(int L, int R, int k = 1, int l = 1, int r = n) { if (L <= l && r <= R) return t[k]; int h = l + r >> 1, o = 0; if (t[k] == 0) t[k << 1] = 0, t[k << 1 | 1] = 0; if (t[k] == r - l + 1) t[k << 1] = h - l + 1, t[k << 1 | 1] = r - h; if (L <= h) o += query(L, R, k << 1, l, h); if (h < R) o += query(L, R, k << 1 | 1, h + 1, r); return o; } int main() { int T, i, x, y, z; scanf("%d", &T); while (T--) { s c a n f ( " % d % d % s % s " , &n, &q, s + 1, f + 1); for (i = 1; i <= q; i++) scanf("%d%d", l + i, r + i); modify(1, n, 0); for (i = 1; i <= n; i++) if (f[i] == '1') modify(i, i, 1); z = 1; for (i = q; i >= 1; i--) { x = q u e r y ( l [ i ] , r[i]); y = r[i] - l[i] + 1 - x; if (x == y) { z = 0; break; } if (x < y) m o d i f y ( l [ i ] , r[i], 0); else m o d i f y ( l [ i ] , r[i], 1); } for (i = 1; i <= n; i++) if ((s[i] - '0') != query(i, i)) z = 0; if (z) cout << "YES\n"; else cout << "NO\n"; } return 0; }
